SECTION 4: VERSION 2 PCB BUILD SPECIFICATION
----------------------------------------------------------------------
  Board diameter   : 100.0 mm +/- 0.1 mm
  Layers           : 120 conductive (= 120 cells of 120-cell)
  f_res_scaled     : ~2.993 GHz (scales 299 MHz for 1m cavity)
  Substrate        : Rogers 4350B, Dk=3.48+/-0.05, Df=0.0037
  Copper           : 0.5 oz = 17 um, Ra < 50 nm
  Layer thickness  : 0.1 mm per layer
  Via count        : 720 plated-through = 720 pentagonal faces
  Via diameter     : 0.20 mm drill, 0.25 mm pad
  Via placement    : H4 symmetry, 10 um tolerance (laser drill)
  Edge traces      : 0.10 mm width, follows 120-cell Schlegel
  Connections      : 1200 edge traces = 1200 edges
  Net lengths      : all equal = 91.3 mm (IPC-2581 netlist)

  Layer map:
    Layer 1        : Vertex ring 1 -- 12 vertices, 5-way traces
    Layers 2-30    : Cell shells 1-29 -- 4 vertices, pentagonal routing
    Layers 31-90   : Core cells 30-89 -- 600-cell interior, 720 vias
    Layers 91-119  : Cell shells 90-118 -- 4 vertices each
    Layer 120      : Vertex ring 2 -- 12 vertices, 5-way traces

  Gerber / ODB++ file list:
    GKO    : Board outline 100mm circle + SMA edge connector cutout
    GTL-G120: 120 copper layers (layer N = Nth dodecahedral cell)
    GTS    : Soldermask, vias exposed for LN2 contact
    DRL    : 720x 0.20mm holes, coordinates from 120-cell projection
    IPC-2581: Netlist, 1200 nets all equal length = 91.3mm

  H4 verification:
    Pre-fab: run H4_sym_check.py on Gerber coordinates
    Max deviation < 5 um (M8D requirement)
    Dihedral angle between adjacent via planes = 116.565 deg exact
    Reject if error > 116.575 deg

SECTION 5: TEST FIXTURE -- M8F PROTOCOL
----------------------------------------------------------------------
  1. Mount  : Invar 36 frame, 720 struts to match via pattern
              Torque to 0.1 N*m
  2. Bond   : Indium at each via pad to Cu dewar wall
              No solder -- breaks H4 symmetry
  3. Pumpdown: < 1e-8 Torr; backfill He 10 mTorr (exchange gas)
  4. Cool   : LN2 to 77 K; verify all 4 Cernox read 77 K +/- 1 K
  5. VNA    : TRL cal with cryo kit at 299.314159 MHz
              S21 phase = delay

